title: Pink String and Sealing Wax [1945 - UK] Ealing thriller

Pink String and Sealing Wax (1945 - UK)

Drama / Thriller

starring . . . . Mervyn Johns, Mary Merrall, Gordon Jackson
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0037991/


Ealing Studios Production Company

An exploration of the clash between two very different worlds in Victorian Brighton. On the one hand the privileged, pious household of respected chemist and Public Analyst Edward Sutton, who rules his family with self-righteous cruelty. On the other hand the seedy underworld occupied by pub landlord's wife Pearl, her brutal, alcoholic husband Joe, and her lover Dan.
